      "content": "i get that, but i already took one about an hour ago because the pain was getting bad and i didnt think it would be a big deal. i feel okay so far, no changes. if i just stick to a low dose like 200mg every few hours, is that still gonna be a major problem for my kidneys or am i overthinking it?",
